rComments: Payman is the best professor I had in 2nd year. His lectures are very clear, at times even better than the (already good) textbook. GO TO OFFICE HOURS if in doubt!! He is very approachable, and even stays longer than required. We had 9 (sometimes difficult) assignments, which I thought was a few too many, but they were VERY good and helpful.
Really great. Clear lectures. Very helpful during office hours. Study your assignments and do the practice problems he posts and you're perfect for the tests and exam.
Take his MAT301. It's very useful. And he's a very caring professor.

Amazing prof! always stayed overtime during office hours to make sure you understood everything. Very good lecturer, clear explanations and his problem sets were very interesting and gave great insight on the topics being learned, moreover he is very fair, if you understand not memorize the given questions you will do well. Hope to have him again.
He's the best but also the worst professor that I've ever met. If you are good at memorizing solutions, go take his courses.

Payman is the best Professor I've had at University. He's so approachable and is great at teaching. He is amazing at understanding people's questions, so lectures and office hours are helpful and at a good pace.
